narrative:
2.38(b) 
   
Miscellaneous. 
The inspector arrived at the facilities offices at 10:40 am but there was no response and a phone message was left. The 
inspector was able to talk to a facility representative at site 001 but they were unable to accompany an inspection at that 
time. Failure to provide access to the facility, animals, and records for inspection is a serious violation of the AWA and 
regulations. Failure to comply may result in enforcement action. 
 
 
End Section
